{"tid":1131332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"神棍幫你做占卜","createTime":"2019-04-29T14:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T12:51:29.000Z","uid":74049,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5e25213cacd5fd1c208c7e6a755ce9b2ccad96","tid":1131332,"uid":74049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"冇話一定好準，純粹太耐冇做占卜想練翻手感<br />\n幫到你就最好，幫唔到既就當大家輕鬆傾下計攞多個意見咁解<br />\n中意可以留言正皮，唔中意亦可嚟留言俾意見等我成長下<br />\n<br />\n［禪卡占卜］<br />\n主要以禪卡為主，以解決問題/困難、釐清問題背後原因為主<br />\n唔占未來，因為樓主覺得占未來冇意思，不如了解清楚而家有咩問題仲實際<br />\n隨需要/樓主心情補Oracle Cards<br />\n<br />\n［發問規矩］<br />\n問題請具體，但可以放心，我睇到問題會同你再傾<br />\n例：<br />\n我同XXX既關係有咩問題&amp;解決方法（唔一定係愛情）<br />\n點解我冇拖拍<br />\n發生左某件事，可以點解決<br />\n<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/Wholelifeisatrap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWholelifeisatrap&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0783d2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Wholelifeisatrap</a><br />\n懶打字，占卜結果基本上會錄音覆<br />\n但請唔好Sd錄音俾我，淨睇文字<br />\n亦可以留言，但有心理準備留言會短過TG好多<br />\n<br />\n人數多既話隨時截，但截前已經搵左我既一定會覆<br />\n最重要請唔好催，有時間就會覆，未覆你就係未到你"},{"pid":"e890d370a4af50084c37dc38c2680b4c02405a2c","tid":1131332,"uid":124058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba186ba09bdd92eb700ae495bbe80f3fcb709c5","tid":1131332,"uid":227637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eabc4f02a91eb443f22854d5f4bc734eb903bdc","tid":1131332,"uid":248837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"有無機會同男朋友復合，謝謝"},{"pid":"897bc9764a5c9e5d11cdf6b278295205b43625a2","tid":1131332,"uid":199799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"