"2019-05-02T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafd35891d615d5e4d7f498c2a97ff02b6df9ff0","tid":1131332,"uid":227878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:31:48.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打 好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499e659213a994ba8b91c56d58d6edbb4a66bf74","tid":1131332,"uid":239300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"男朋友對我忽冷忽熱<br />\n咩原因？應該點解決？<br />\nThanks🙏🏻"},{"pid":"387ca735eb7860771689c82218707dead97259de","tid":1131332,"uid":232709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74545f50cb16a39d9aeb10c9c5df59a3f25982c8","tid":1131332,"uid":74049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96f4249af4f6237e1632019be209cdc6dbda1fe9","tid":1131332,"uid":159917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"同前度有冇機會一齊返或者佢點諗我呢？<br />\nThx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"冇話唔可以 但你要主動啲 關心佢多啲<br />\n但結果一次 大家精神上根本溝通唔到"},{"pid":"bf02da51a39c9318fecc7525c3c4d3a08df9679f","tid":1131332,"uid":74049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8cb2c160390b8f0c764bba2cb090c8fa79c9cbe","tid":1131332,"uid":223598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"我老豆係咪唔會再有工做 我頂唔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"難啲 有都係短期 做唔長"},{"pid":"8d965ff1ff3fc77dec0baa35bc3791788cafe864","tid":1131332,"uid":74049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f5261ee215a0340003f9328094688268ffc436","tid":1131332,"uid":93935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"re